  "name": "Release Notes v3.13.7 - Accounting Integrations",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"release-notes-v3-13-7-accounting-integrations\">Release Notes v3.13.7 - Accounting Integrations</h1>\n<p><span><strong>Release Date:</strong><span> </span>22nd June 2021</span></p>\n<p>In this update we've made several improvements and resolutions as part of our commitment to continuous evolution and improvement to Retail Express.</p>\n<hr></hr><h3 data-id=\"exclude-transaction-types-from-xero\"><a name=\"transaction-types\"></a>Exclude Transaction Types from Xero</h3>\n<p>We have added the ability to configure which transactions should be included/excluded from the Upload to Xero.</p>\n<p>Within the Xero Integration configuration in Retail Express (Settings &gt; Integrations &gt; Xero) we've added a new \"Transaction Types\" tab. To exclude a Transaction Type from Xero simply untick the option and click <strong>Save all</strong>.</p>\n<div>\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>These will all be ticked by default to match the existing integration behaviour</p>\n</div>\n<p><img alt=\"xero_integration_settings.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZNEAY.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZNEAY.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZNEAY.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZNEAY.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZNEAY.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZNEAY.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZNEAY.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZNEAY.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<hr></hr><h3 data-id=\"improvements-and-resolutions\"><a name=\"resolutions\" id=\"resolutions\"></a>Improvements and Resolutions</h3>\n<ul><li>Added the ability to configure <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Configuring-Payment-Types\">Payment Types</a> to be synchronised as a consolidated daily total or individual payments (available for both Xero and MYOB)<br/><img alt=\"mceclip1 - 2023-07-09T185530.393.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZXEAY.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZXEAY.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZXEAY.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZXEAY.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZXEAY.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZXEAY.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZXEAY.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfZXEAY.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Resolved an issue where in specific circumstances the <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Xero-Integration-Setup\">Xero integration</a> created duplicate invoices</li></ul><p> </p>",
